a match for him.

555
00:35:16,610 --> 00:35:17,650
Young Master Lin.

556
00:35:22,130 --> 00:35:24,570
You heard Master Lin's

557
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,340
dying words,

558
00:35:28,020 --> 00:35:28,820
didn't you?

559
00:35:28,937 --> 00:35:30,780
