577
00:36:39,380 --> 00:36:40,090
Yan Shao?

578
00:36:42,020 --> 00:36:42,820
Yan Shao!

579
00:36:43,340 --> 00:36:44,130
Yan Shao!

580
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,650
Be quiet.

581
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:48,820
