589
00:37:23,940 --> 00:37:25,300
(I would protect you for life.)

590
00:37:28,380 --> 00:37:30,530
(Am I a burden to you?)

591
00:37:33,780 --> 00:37:35,380
(Do you just want me)

592
00:37:36,380 --> 00:37:38,820
