623
00:40:04,210 --> 00:40:05,050
Let's take a break.

624
00:40:05,380 --> 00:40:05,730
Come.

625
00:40:06,460 --> 00:40:08,340
Hold still!

626
00:40:08,582 --> 00:40:09,610
